{"tid":812260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那高鐵飯盒發霉　乘客未為意吃掉一半上吐下瀉","createTime":"2018-09-09T13:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T16:54:09.000Z","uid":51271,"like":138,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"d9b151d76be0863ee064b9daf77c34ac52149b94","tid":812260,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T13:23:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180909/s00004/1536487807411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180909%2Fs00004%2F1536487807411&d=YyJV2okEaSWCeIsyrmcBL7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5144030f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180909%2Fs00004%2F1536487807411&h=cb00d55c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180909/s00004/1536487807411</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢兩名市民周六（8日）乘搭高鐵途中，在餐車上購買飯盒，打開驚見食物嚴重發霉。其中一人吃了一半才發現變質，事後不適嘔吐腹瀉。車長表示，公司正調查原因。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，乘客祝先生及夏先生，由北京乘搭高鐵到武漢，車上買了兩個飯盒，不料發現飯盒發霉。夏先生沒為意下，整盒飯吃了一半，事後出現嘔吐腹瀉。祝先生隨即向工作人員投訴，車長就事件道歉並安排退還80元餐費，以及重新送上新套餐，但遭到拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n祝先生指：「本來肚子很餓，但看到高鐵上竟然有這樣發霉的食物，以後再也不敢吃了。」他稱不需要賠償，但飯盒不僅賣給他一人，「這種情況肯定不是個別例子」，要求列車公司調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n餐飲公司事後以電話短信向祝先生道歉，並安排負責人洽談後續事宜。飯盒由上海新成食品有限公司華洲路分公司生產，內地傳媒暫未能向其聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180909/s00004/69d04cb1eec5be4da71274d805323dfe.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180909%2Fs00004%2F69d04cb1eec5be4da71274d805323dfe.jpg&d=YyJV2okEaSWCeIsyrmcBL7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=3ef8a3ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180909%2Fs00004%2F69d04cb1eec5be4da71274d805323dfe.jpg&h=4f2b4beb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180909/s00004/69d04cb1eec5be4da71274d805323dfe.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180909/s00004/69ddfc09ad1f7980ed0bcaec75f6133d.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180909%2Fs00004%2F69ddfc09ad1f7980ed0bcaec75f6133d.jpg&d=YyJV2okEaSWCeIsyrmcBL7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=67deeee1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180909%2Fs00004%2F69ddfc09ad1f7980ed0bcaec75f6133d.jpg&h=359bbd85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180909/s00004/69ddfc09ad1f7980ed0bcaec75f6133d.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180909/s00004/69dae32ebdec3feb33e4f1d4036fe053.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180909%2Fs00004%2F69dae32ebdec3feb33e4f1d4036fe053.jpg&d=YyJV2okEaSWCeIsyrmcBL7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1f03b5ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180909%2Fs00004%2F69dae32ebdec3feb33e4f1d4036fe053.jpg&h=daa4e704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180909/s00004/69dae32ebdec3feb33e4f1d4036fe053.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"5d0e772712f30724c8b569a9d50b2e22b8f7fbeb","tid":812260,"uid":51271,"like":196,"dislike":0,"score":196,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T13:23:46.000Z","msg":"呢盒狗飯都要40蚊人仔，唔怪得落到香港要食100蚊盒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c766896feed3801d33f612b524387a51d142c07","tid":812260,"uid":127292,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T13:25:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b936956d2398836f736ffd3b7aecf554651c1cf","tid":812260,"uid":42188,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09